description: Sunseed Sunnatural Select spring harvest timothy nutritious grass hay that provides an excellent source of long strand fiber without the excess protein, energy and calcium found in the legume hays, such as alfalfa. Some pets, particularly adult rabbits, have lower requirements for protein, energy and calcium, making spring harvest the ideal forage selection for these animals. Timothy hay is widely recommended by veterinarians as an ideal fiber source, necessary to keep the digestive systems of herbivores functioning properly. Alternate with sweet grass to increase variety. Perfect for rabbit, guinea pig and chinchilla. Its weighs 56-ounce. It includes 3 grass hay pouch per pack.
